<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id774b6f9e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410y–1a"><num value="410y–1a">§ 410y–1a.</num><heading> Boundary revision</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The boundaries of the park are revised to include approximately 600 additional acres.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id774b6f9f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/625/tIII/s320">Pub. L. 95–625, title III, § 320</ref>, <date date="1978-11-10">Nov. 10, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3488">92 Stat. 3488</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/96/199/tI/s101/c">Pub. L. 96–199, title I, § 101(c)</ref>, <date date="1980-03-05">Mar. 5, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/68">94 Stat. 68</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id774b6fa0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id774b6fa1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id774b6fa2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was enacted as part of the National Parks and Recreation Act of 1978, and not as part of the Chesapeake and Ohio Canal Development Act which comprises this subchapter.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id774b6fa3-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1980—<ref href="/us/pl/96/199">Pub. L. 96–199</ref> struck out proviso that additions to the park as authorized by this section shall not include any properties located between 30th Street and Thomas Jefferson Street in the northwest section of the District of Columbia.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
